          "description": "I am a new patient and had an amazing experience from beginning to end. They say your first appointment will take longer than normal; I figured it was just because they needed to take X-rays and things to develop a baseline, but it\u2019s also because they really take the time to educate you on what\u2019s going on with your teeth. Both the hygienist and Dr. Mohajer are extremely knowledgeable and made it clear they care. Maria at reception is also so friendly, helpful, and efficient. Excellent all around!",
